export LANG="${LANG:-en_US.UTF-8}"
export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/sh}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/bhbuilder/benchpress}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-bhbuilder}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/bhbuilder}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/usr/bin:/bin}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/bhbuilder/.local/lib:}"
export _="${_:-/home/bhbuilder/bohrium-by-night/run_benchmark.py}"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-5748ffed-d219-4848-9a5c-6524ccd9b423.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Gauss Elimination'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = node

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = gpu
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so
timing = false

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/bhbuilder/.local/include -I/home/bhbuilder/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/bhbuilder/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/bhbuilder/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/bhbuilder/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
template_path = /home/bhbuilder/.local/share/bohrium/templates
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_ve_cpu.so

libs = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
include = /home/bhbuilder/.local/share/bohrium/include
work_goup_size_1dx = 128
work_goup_size_2dx = 32
work_goup_size_2dy = 4
work_goup_size_3dx = 32
work_goup_size_3dy = 2
work_goup_size_3dz = 2
kernel = both
compile = async
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]

impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]

impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]

impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu

 /usr/bin/time -v -o /home/bhbuilder/benchpress/bh-job-5748ffed-d219-4848-9a5c-6524ccd9b423.sh-0.time python benchmark/Python/gauss.py --size=1000 --bohrium=True 1> /home/bhbuilder/benchpress/bh-job-5748ffed-d219-4848-9a5c-6524ccd9b423.sh-0.out 2> /home/bhbuilder/benchpress/bh-job-5748ffed-d219-4848-9a5c-6524ccd9b423.sh-0.err
